Another (verbose) option would be to use a MultiBinding on the ContentTemplate property instead of using a DataTemplateSelector.
<br />
<br />&lt;ContentControl.ContentTemplate&gt;
<br />  &lt;MultiBinding Converter="..."&gt;
<br />    &lt;Binding RelativeSource="{RelativeSource Self}" /&gt;
<br />    &lt;Binding Path="Content.Age" RelativeSource="{RelativeSource Self}" /&gt;
<br />  &lt;/MultiBinding&gt;
<br />&lt;/ContentControl.ContentTemplate&gt;
